Notes: Rochester downs Eastern Connecticut, 71-66, in NCAA 1st-round game Friday
at Scranton's Long Center; Baroody leads Yellowjackets with 15 points
McNelis adds 13 and Porter contributes 12 points and 11 rebounds; McFetridge
and Morey pace ECSU with 19 points apiece
Game.Officials: Kevin Farlow,  Terry Glass,  Michelle Rolko; T. Brazill-Alt.
